	   <tr><td colspan=2>Spirit of Cheetah has a long refresh time.&nbsp;&nbsp;It is 10 minutes I do believe.  Basically, after you memorize it, you will have to wait for 10 minutes before you can use it.  Several spells are this way to prevent abuse.  The divine aura line and harvest come to mind.  It used to be zoning would refresh Cheetah and make it ready again, but as far as I know, that no longer works =/<br><br>In essence, you will need to dedicate a spell slot for this emergency spell.  Personally, I do not think it is worth it as I can count on one hand the number of times in almost two years I have used it.  One of those was racing a Bard through Butcherblock with my Druid =)  It has never saved my character's life, although some people swear by it =)<br><br>Gorthin Spiritcaller<br>51 Shaman BB<br>Drindal<br>43 Monk BB<br>&nbsp;<br> </td></tr>
