 power of the pp)<br><br>Walruses:  Seems I'm KoS...and I mean REALLY KoS to the walruses in EW.  Kid you not, I can sit to med with a full group of five others circled around me, and I can see in the distance a herd of walruses running in fast as a kunark rhino and they'll all come STRAIGHT FOR ME.  Is this a shaman thing or just a "Badjur has bad walrus faction" thing?  It does make grouping for man o wars in EW interesting...never a dull moment.  I relocated to DL last night, but look forward to getting back to EW to round up some walrus meat for the ultimate payback  :)   Walrus steaks anyone?  (that is if the walrus meat can be prepared)<br><br>Snow Bunnies:  Has anyone else heard that the snow bunnies drop a rare ring?  I've heard this rumored, but as yet to have it confirmed.  In the meantime  ALL SNOW BUNNIES MUST DIE!!<br><br>/em apologizes for the lengthiness of her post, but she is at work and bored silly and needed a distraction.<br><br>Take care all!<br>&nbsp;<br>Badjur<br>Oracle of Novus Invictus<br>(Druzzil Ro)<br><br>Aepox Weeblatter<br>51 Dwarf Warrior</td></tr>
