	   <td id=headerrow align=right><span id=notbold>Score</span>: Default<span id=notbold>[2.00]</span></td></tr>
	   <tr><td colspan=2>Damage Over Time (DOT) spells give us the most damage for mana used.&nbsp;&nbsp;However they take time to deliever this damage.  Poision based dots take 42 sec to deliver full damage.  Sickness based dots take 2 min.  Most often in a group the fight will not last long enough for sickness based dots to be mana efficent.  One exception is on multipul pull where you can root and sickness dot one of the mobs.  Most of the time Poision Dots are the most effective way a shaman can use mana in a group to do damage.<br>&nbsp;<br> </td></tr>
	   <tr><td colspan=1 >&nbsp;</td><td align=right valign=bottom>
