	   <tr><td colspan=2>depends on what race you are.... For trolls and Ogres i'd advise going to feerrott, getting a couple of buffs from someone waiting for a fear raid and soloing the yellow skeletons at the skele camps. All my ogres (i have at least 1 of each class an ogre can be) did this from 4-9 in less then a day of playing. I then got some more uber buffs and solo'd orcs in Sro. When those buffs wore out i went to Nro and got in a derv group. That takes you to about level 14 i believe. You can then go to Highpass and kill orcs. They drop chain armor and a few decent rare loots from rare spawns. This will take you to 20.<br><br>Please rate this post.. i like input on what people think about my advice =)<br><br>Nitsujlak Barshemguud Ogre Shammy of War <br>Prexus Server<br>Send a tell anytime! <br>&nbsp;<br></td></tr>
